snippet.title: How do Fish Breath Underwater? #shorts
snippet.description:
#shorts
For "HUGE" Discount on 3D Animation Course, Call: +91-99830-83303 or Click here üëâüèª https://professorofhow.com

How do Fish Breath Underwater? #shorts 

If someone drowned your head in water, nothing will be more important for you than taking your head out for breathing. But how does a fish spends its whole life inside water? Double tap the screen and let's understand the science behind fish breathing inside water.
A fish consists of two gills on both sides of its head behind its eyes, these gills remain covered by the operculum. The breathing process in fish takes place in 2 steps.
First - The opercula and the mouth of fish both combined work as a pump, which makes water move inside the mouth of the fish through gills and takes it out of the water, this pumping is called buccal pumping.
Second - When water moves through gills, because of the numerous capillaries present in the gills, they work as a filter. These filters absorb oxygen from the water and drain the water and CO2 out of the body.
The absorbed oxygens get bonded with hemoglobin and reach the entire body and completed the breathing process.
However, the fishes like whales and dolphins cannot breathe underwater, they can remain inside the water for a long time without breathing and approach the surface of the water to inhale oxygen.

snippet.title: [NEP] PMGC 2022 Grand Finals | Day 1 | PUBG MOBILE Global Championship
snippet.description:
The 2022 PUBG MOBILE Global Championship Grand Finals Day 1 is here! We will witness the epic battles between the world's best #PUBGMOBILE teams in the #PMGC2022 Grand Finals from January 6 to 8 to crown the champion in Jakarta, Indonesia! 

16 teams will compete against each other, but in the end, only one will be the champion! Get ready for breathtaking competition between the best of the best! Every match, every drop, every rotation, and every elimination is critical! There is no room for mistakes with the stakes this high! Which team will prove today that they got what it takes to #BETHEONE?

The first day of the PMGC Grand Finals starts on January 6 at 11:00 AM (UTC +0)! To become part of this epic saga, cheer for your team in the chat, and show your support and respect!

snippet.description:
Presenting "Jumla," a soulful tune with a love story at its core. The words for this song were written by Aman Neelsagar and me. I composed the song, produced it, and performed it. Many aspects of Karnali Province and far-western culture, including the Khas dialect, can be found in this song. This swoon-worthy tune features Miss Pabi and Roshan KC. This music video was filmed across Jumla in several stunning settings. The music video is directed by Shishir Khati.

"Promote Internal Tourism"

snippet.title: Sushant KC - Hawa Le
snippet.description:
I finished my show in the UK, boarded a plane, and got off in Doha. Just as I was ready to head home, I tested positive for covid and what should have been a few hours of transit ended up being a ten-day quarantine. In the boredom of isolation I opened logic on my laptop and what I ended up with was the beat to this song. I got back to Nepal and I scribbled and scribbled till I came up with the lyrics. Then I hit up my friend Nayan and asked him to tag along for a trip to Pokhara. We didn‚Äôt take any heavy equipment with us. Nor did we take a schedule.
